<article id="post-40" class="post-40 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Elevator Sump Pump &#038; Oil Alarm System</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>R.M.C. Supply Co. offers <a title="Elevator Sump Pump" href="http://www.rmcsupply.com/new/elevator-sump-pump-products/">Elevator Sump Pump and Oil Alarm Systems</a> designed to prevent pumping oil into a municipal wastewater system, in the event of a leak or spill.</p>
<p>Our systems are designed by an elevator industry expert with over 26 years of experience. Each system is manufactured using only code compliant components and delivered as a “ready to install” solution. It is the easiest to install of any product of its kind available on the market.</p>
<p>The systems are specifically manufactured for <a title="Installation" href="http://www.rmcsupply.com/new/elevator-sump-pump-installation/">ease of installation</a>. <strong>Every system is tested prior to shipment.</strong></p>
<p>We invite you to browse this site to learn about our product and please feel free to <a title="Contact Us" href="http://www.rmcsupply.com/new/elevator-sump-pump-contact-us/">contact us</a> with any comments or inquiries.</p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
